{"type": "article", "id": 2209, "title": "家酿酒套件", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:34:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052222534NDR79eroyZkslCq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这个冬天，你可以在家里藏下一瓶自酿的酒招待好友了。Norse Hutchens 近日推出了一系列酿酒套件，不仅包含酿酒所需的原料与工具，还附上了贴心的操作说明。多种类型的酒能够满足不同人群的需求，你可以选择美容养颜、补肾养胃的蜂蜜酒，也可以试试墨西哥的果酒 MOONSHINE ，日本清酒与葡萄酒的制作配方均有提供。定价 30-140 美元不等，</span><a href=\"http://www.uncommongoods.com/sets/homemade-alcohol-kits\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134918kC49Fh7xPwKNXYtb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134919UOXlDILNFvPeZ5HV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134920ubq4hPij9UCZt87m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261349203OrqxvsbfUTWVnJj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134921IvroixA7X89FGZwW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}